Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:10.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,My First Errand - Can't Wait Until Summer Special
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:17.22,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\move(-6.577,304.523,163.052,302.536,2,300)}My First Errand staff room
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:14.30,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(479.345,235.545)\fad(200,0)}Tokoro George
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The spring special. \N That's not something to miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on it will get warmer \N and the summer is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And they grow up so fast before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The smiles of children, \N well there are tears too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are all things of passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:33.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The first smile on our program today comes from the big adventure of the coconut daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:36.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,1 hour from Toshin by train.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(336,305.28)}Saitama ● Ogawa City
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:41.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The first errand is in Saitama Prefecture, Ogawa which overlooks the mountains of Chichibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:47.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today is open school day for parents whose children go to the kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs16\pos(119.802,301.586)}Narrator: \N Chikaishi Shinsuke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:50.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Among the mothers and fathers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:53.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,there is a mother carrying a baby on her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:01:00.12,OrangeFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(623.032,245.489)\fad(200,0)}Ko\N ko\N na
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:01:00.12,OrangeFill,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\fs18\pos(503.248,263.959)}5 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:58.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kokona has become serious after becoming an older sister as of last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.42,0:01:01.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to help her busy mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:01.48,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.88,0:01:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(457.342,35.632)\fad(200,0)}Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:03.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother is still 22 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:05.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.44,0:01:08.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That means... if Kokona is 5 years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194.948,319.44)}Father. 19 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(474.588,328.674)}Mother. 17 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:15.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. The mother gave birth to Kokona when she was 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:16.06,OrangeFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(516.473,296.586)}Shrine visit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:20.20,OrangeFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(517.089,294.739)}Wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:18.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They got married when Kokona was 1 year old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:21.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,\NWhen Kokona was 3, the mother went through her coming-of-age ceremony.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:25.42,OrangeFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(518.937,294.74)}Coming of age \N ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:25.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Nevermind all that. \N Kokona is such a great name. How did she think of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.24,0:01:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was pregnant at 17
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a tanning parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.84,0:01:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(319.985,315.746)}Tan-pa = Tanning parlor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:35.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I didn't have a name
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(321.217,311.436)}Cosmetic coconut oil
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and you know the coconut oil that makes a nice smell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(338.464,311.436)}Falling in love with coconuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.34,0:01:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and I fell in love with the smell,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought of making her name like coconut.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(283.028,305.896)}Kokona
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(373.573,306.512)\fade(0,400)}tsu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.862,306.511)}=
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(412.377,305.896)}Kokona
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:02:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\move(412.377,305.896, 330, 270, 0, 800)}Kokona
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that coconut would be too strange so I advised my grandparents.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.64,0:01:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They suggested to use the characters meaning "Peace at Heart" where the peace is the same as in the Shouwa era.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.14,0:01:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What a great name you've given her is what people told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.54,0:02:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You must surely have given it a lot of thought. Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:10.04,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB31000&\pos(576.836,142.137)\fad(300,0)}Little brother
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:10.06,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB31000&\pos(625.495,338.525)\fad(300,0)}Hinata \N 8 months \Nold
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:05.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The baby is a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the first time celebrating Children's Day since his birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants prove herself for her tiny baby brother, so her mother has asked us to help with her first errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- You can go and do it, right? \N - Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.54,0:02:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- You can do it, right? \N - I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,At the stand ....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening? Look me in the eyes and listen!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:26.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mother is serious about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you ask the bus driver when you get on board?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:33.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So she's going on a bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:34.96,WhiteOrangeBorder,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this bus drive to Ogawa station?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this bus drive to Ogawa station?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:41.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What does she have to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You know they sell small versions of those carp streamers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For Hinata's Children's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to buy one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep it a secret from Hinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:51.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The bus comes twice an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:54.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The errand includes donuts and tofu made from Okara in front of the station,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:54.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(310.836,32.171)\fs14}TN: Okara is a residue from tofu making. It's a by-product which gives it certain qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:56.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,cake and carp streamer cookie from the cake shop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:03:01.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and various items from the grilled meat shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:03.22,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\fs20}Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.26,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\fs20}That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Karaage \N - Do you have any Karaage, Bang Bang?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(310.836,32.171)\fs14}TN: Karaage is fried chicken. Bang Bang is another kind of chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any Karaage, Bang Bang?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do you have any Karaage, Bang Bang? \N - Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:15.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yes, she can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you cry if you become scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:21.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you come back crying from being scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is her method to turn on Kokona's ambition switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Say "thank you" if you ask someone about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be a bit late. The grill shop is always so slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't come back drunk. \N - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:46.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An energetic Kokona is dashing forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,One two, one two, one two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:49.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:53.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I really do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:58.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At that time even the mother
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:04:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is wondering if she can do it by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time for her to go through a first errand. Either for herself or someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:10.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kokona remembers that mother packed her a rice ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:13.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Holding tightly where her mother has squeezed the rice ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:18.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yes, now I've received power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The bus only comes twice an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Walking to the bus stop usually takes 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:33.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She was given 3 times the time to make it there. 45 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:37.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So she is there ahead of time. \N There is still 35 minutes until the next bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mother told her to wait in the shop in front of the bus stop in such a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Is the bus coming today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the bus will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going shopping by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You are going shopping by yourself? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:56.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just a little bit of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:05:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom told me I can buy 1 candy item.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I have money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Having spent time shopping the bus might arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- You can cross here. \N - Yes, I can cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:11.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You're already going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:16.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It usually takes time to choose a piece of candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:18.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But she was only in the shop for 5 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the bus is here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the bus is here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:26.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There's still 30 minutes until the bus is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see the bus at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It totally isn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Still not seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not doing anything and just waiting \Nis the hardest thing for Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after she is done eating the onigiri (rice ball).
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't understand how slow time passes or how many minutes are left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The staff is in the same situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The shop owner has been watching from inside the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going shopping alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,By yourself? You're so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking of riding the bus tomorrow. So I came by to check the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you wait a little bit more?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait a little more. Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me some. Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.30,0:06:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And after waiting a bit more, the bus came.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:30.16,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's coming, coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:31.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kokona. The bus is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The bus isn't coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:35.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:40.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kokona is so surprised that it is suddenly there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:45.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Finally. She gets to board it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:47.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The ones who are most relieved are the cameramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:04.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The bus arrives after 10 minutes. \NMuch less than the waiting time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:07.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Paying the money just like she was told by her mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:10.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She said it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:13.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The first place she is heading to is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I must go to the Okara donuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In this shop they make various kinds of donuts and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,they recently started making Okara donuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, do you have cheap tofu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheap tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheap tofu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There are all kinds of tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes. \N - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:37.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother made her get the most common tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:40.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,These are donuts made from Okara.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She was told to buy various types.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:49.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And when she is done choosing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:52.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She dropped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:56.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry. \NBut she isn't getting scolded by the shop attendants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I will hold it so please take.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:01.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama said to take 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:07.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She is letting Kokona do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, fo-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:13.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kokona is so nervous because of her blunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:15.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This one looks look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:19.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The shop attendant gives the dejected Kokona
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:22.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,a pink balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:31.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She was so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:34.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Please greet people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's what she is told by her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going shopping by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You are shopping by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I was at the donut place and now I'm heading for the cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that so? \N - Make sure you take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes. Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:53.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If you greet people they will be kind to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Heading for the cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:09:00.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Rather than the cake shop she is more concerned about what to buy from the grilled meat shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang Bang chicken and Yakitori perchance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:05.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not Yakitori, chicken Tsukune.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang Bang chicken...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:10.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And Tsukune perchance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do my very best...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to get confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang Bang chicken
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:21.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:24.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is a bus stop she's never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:27.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While she's been saying Bang Bang she's left the trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.18,Studio,,0,0,0,,This is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.18,0:09:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a lost child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And yet she keeps walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Fried chicken...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang Bang chicken Tsukune
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She remembered Tsukune.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang Bang chicken Tsukune
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it was. Bang Bang chicken and Tsukune.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going shopping by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Shopping? Where to? \N - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you already shopped at the cake shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Not yet. \N - Not yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Pekochan Cake Shop was that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:09.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was it again? \N It was that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:15.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This way. Peko. Ca-. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,, When coming here she always does the usual greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake shake shake. He-hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She was asked to purchase a polar bear cake and carp streamer cookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Polar bear cake, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:44.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358.877,275.784)}Mr. Best Friend Bear
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:45.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This one is for Kokona. And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:47.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And a cookie for her little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Since today is a holiday, the box is Children's Day-themed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:58.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since they are going to grandpa's house, she was told to buy a carp streamer if they have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:00.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thankfully it isn't sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought it-*bounce*.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:12.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Invigorated again, she is now heading for the grilled meat shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:13.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she will remember the song?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang Bang chicken Tsukune.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:21.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the shop she goes to with her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm shopping by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- You came by yourself? \N - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yes, that song you've been singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang Bang for one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Bang Bang meal. \N - And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,5 pieces of Kashira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:36.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fs15\pos(326.849,20.163)}TN: Kashira is from the tender part of the chicken breast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,5 pieces of Kashira, 1 Bang Bang meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:43.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The song became a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But she remembers when she ate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one is round?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a Dango.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukene?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, 5 of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you are shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- By myself.  \N - Hi, Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina, isn't it great that Kokona is shopping by herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yep, all by myself.  \N - You came by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- You can do that? \N - Yes, of course I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You are walking by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I took the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kokona...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you came by yourself I will give you a Tsukune.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the fried chicken?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside mummy's tummy there is yet another baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet another? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why your mother isn't drinking alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's purchased Bang Bang, Tsukune and Kashira but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,she forgot the first item in the song. Karaage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:44.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's exhausted from carrying the purchased items.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:46.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What? Beer!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:48.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No, no, no. It's juice, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about being tired,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it was exhausting, I tell ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that it took me so long to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It was quick, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is that it took some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:05.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Can I complain a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, mama drew it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She drew it so I can go shopping for Hinata and come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinata, Mama, Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And the one in her tummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:23.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I will become the eldest sister of them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Customer, don't drink until dawn. \N You still have shopping to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:33.40,Studio,,0,0,0,, Are they old geezers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes. \N - Remember to greet your mother from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes. \N - Okay? \N - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do your best.  \N - Yes.  \N - Do your best, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do your best.  \N - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been 2 hours and 20 minutes since she left the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,, It's the 5 o'clock bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:56.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(310.836,32.171)\fs14}TN: It signals all over Japan that children should head home for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,At the ♩ bottom of ♪ the mountain ♪ what bell is ringing. 🎶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(310.836,32.171)\fs14}TN: Loosely based on the song Kanenonaruoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:22.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Grandpa and grandma's house is the mother's childhood home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:26.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother went ahead and is preparing for the celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:31.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother is making Inari Sushi in the style of carp streamers (koinobori).
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:34.26,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\pos(104.147,24.284)}This mother can make all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kokona, you came! \N You were able to do it by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought carp streamers for Hinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:48.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You thought it might be sold out but it was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it scary? Or was it not scary at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You were able to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kokona was able to go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:04.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hinata, you sure have a fine sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that this one is cute so I bought it for Hinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you greet Pekochan today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this. Mum did her best and made this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see carp streamers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- I do. \N - You can see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are carp streamers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:30.48,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mama, here. \N - This is so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Karaage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say Karaage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- I forgot. \N - You forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevermind. Let's eat next because you did your best. \N It's okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Today I did my best, cheers. \N - Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:55.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Getting praised by everyone. She did a lot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it? How, how, how, how?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:16:00.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just wait, mama. I will praise you in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:08.00,TextOver,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE61EDB&\fad(200,200)\pos(290.819,350.272)}Moriguchi Hiroko \N Singer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When you think of spring \N all kinds of things seem so shiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And above all the shining smiles of children are unmatchable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:20.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next up is a bald rebellious kid growing up on an orange orchard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(337.144,305.52)}Mizaki ● Nango　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:23.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Blue ocean, blue skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:28.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The sunshine paradise, Miyazaki prefecture. \N We've arrived at the city of Nango.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:31.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The entire mountainside is all grandpa's orange orchard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:35.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,During the harvest all the relatives help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:38.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Taking in all the sun along with the oranges,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:45.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,there is a boy who also takes in a lot of sun and is brought up full of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:49.64,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6E2510&\pos(105.519,164.271)}Yuuta. 4 years and \N 3 months old.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:48.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,4 year old Yuuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:51.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Getting the hang of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it in mother's basket next.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:56.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's sneaking out of chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you thirsty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tea. \N - You haven't worked that much yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:09.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's been ignoring his mother lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:14.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When it comes to picking oranges it's best to ask grandpa who knows everything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:26.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Bringing up a child requires a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:34.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother will not lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 10 already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the errand is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, it's 10 now. \N - Okay, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not time to go home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go drink some tea and then
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you can go and make orange juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,By myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.22,0:17:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:58.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The errand entails heading home and making orange juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting the oranges he harvested in the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Remember to make orange juice. \N - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home by yourself and make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:15.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For the mother who thinks that he never listens to her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:18.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,it's a bit unusual how fast he took off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:24.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He does what he is told. When it comes to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:30.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will he come back again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, he will be back. After finishing his errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:38.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother trusts Yuuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so overwhelmed by how well-behaved his response was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.90,0:18:47.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He listened to his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You are making me cry as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.16,0:18:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Since this is my first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a bit uneasy but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:19:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,since he left he didn't need to look back even once so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so... so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:08.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's too good to be true. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:12.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Once he is home there are games and and a TV. \N No way he will be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Home. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's humming to himself while unlocking the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:22.96,Studio,,0,0,0,,Scribbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:25.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are all the work of Yuuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:34.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We thought that he would start playing as soon as he got home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But these are the instruments for making orange juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:40.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I was talking nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:43.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He came back to properly do his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:46.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Things surely change when you become 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:50.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What? Did you forget something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:55.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's leaving for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:20:00.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hold up, that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:09.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He found a neighborhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:12.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's Maro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:18.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The play is escalating.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:21.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:24.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What happened to coming back after pressing the juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:29.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seems like there will be none of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:32.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Waiting for 40 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:34.52,Studio,,0,0,0,,Poor mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure takes a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.54,0:20:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't very useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried cause we don't know how he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:51.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The only one who knows how he is is Maro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Close to an hour has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:21:01.28,Studio,,0,0,0,,- He isn't pressing juice. \N- He forgot all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:02.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:06.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's playing by himself. I wonder if he will press the juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:13.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What!? You only came to take your hat? \N Your mom is waiting. She is trusting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:15.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.66,0:21:19.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The phone is ringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:24.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He loves to answer the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta, it's your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta, how is the juice coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Still.. It's already finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.22,0:21:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Still... Finished??
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.84,0:21:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you fill it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's full of juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's full? Hurry up and come back, Yuuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.98,0:21:49.60,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back with it. Everyone is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yep. \N - Hurry up and bring it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes. \N - Yes, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.32,0:22:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer was good but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he has made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- He said he's made it? \N - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:12.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since he said he's already made it he better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.84,0:22:15.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hey, you can't stand on the place where you eat food.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.14,0:22:19.48,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's onigiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:23.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mother has left it for lunch for when they get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.10,0:22:27.04,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Because he ran. \N - Yeah, must be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.40,0:22:31.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He started eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:33.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Something is different about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.10,0:22:35.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yuuta has noticed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.22,0:22:38.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yuuta who is afraid of ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.78,0:22:41.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's never been home alone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.66,0:22:44.42,Studio,,0,0,0,,- What's wrong? \N - He's hiding in a cool place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:51.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh right! Mom can't yell at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.16,0:22:58.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It seems he can break higher things as he gets taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:00.30,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.64,0:23:04.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What? He's taking the water gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.46,0:23:07.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What about pressing the juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.00,0:23:10.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Maro, you are in danger. Run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.36,0:23:19.06,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.52,0:23:21.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.52,0:23:24.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's as if his mother is watching him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Yuuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.16,0:23:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.14,0:23:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, press the juice and bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about your protection charm?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The protection charm? It's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have it on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.78,0:23:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.62,0:23:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lies. I can see that you don't have it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She can see?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.84,0:23:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.84,0:23:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you're wearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.60,0:23:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.86,0:23:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you wearing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.02,0:24:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm wearing it. \N - You are? Then the orange juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.32,0:24:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't pressed the orange juice yet. \N Make sure to do it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.26,0:24:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you press it and bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.72,0:24:11.72,Studio,,0,0,0,,The way he's holding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.72,0:24:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up. Make it and bring it. Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.94,0:24:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.90,0:24:19.04,Studio,,0,0,0,,He cut her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.54,0:24:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He cut me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.32,0:24:25.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The otherwise quiet house is now ringing with the scolding echo of the mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.62,0:24:28.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped. Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.40,0:24:32.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He usually is happy to help make the juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.04,0:24:34.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's why the mother has chosen this to be the errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.20,0:24:38.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's a child who doesn't do what he doesn't want to. But does the things he loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.80,0:24:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Round and round and round.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.80,0:24:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Round and round and round.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.86,0:24:46.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's even putting ice in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.76,0:24:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting in the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.14,0:24:56.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother said to come back with a full container.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.44,0:24:58.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It fills up easier because of the ice but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.38,0:25:00.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There's not enough for a full container.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.42,0:25:03.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yep, a couple drops of lemon juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.88,0:25:08.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,One cup of syrup.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.10,0:25:11.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The taste is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.54,0:25:14.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't drink all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.38,0:25:23.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The volume is small but it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.78,0:25:31.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Starting at 10 o'clock, noon has passed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.18,0:25:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm late. I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.04,0:25:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He finally came.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.00,0:25:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought it with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.34,0:25:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.54,0:25:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.58,0:25:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta, did you do it all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.26,0:25:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.84,0:26:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad. Thank you, Yuuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.78,0:26:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We were waiting. Grandpa and grandma too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.88,0:26:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and let's drink some juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.38,0:26:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,, - I brought everyone. \N - You brought everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.34,0:26:13.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there is enough for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.74,0:26:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a sample for everyone. Freshly squeezed orange juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.54,0:26:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Cheers. \N - Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.00,0:26:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.34,0:26:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The ice has melted just the right amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.58,0:26:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious, Yuuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.68,0:26:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've become invigorated.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.68,0:26:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.80,0:26:45.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They went from scolding him to praising him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.86,0:26:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(323,292)}Kagoshima    ●     Soo
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.08,0:26:53.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To an almost unbelievable extent we've managed to track down an errand genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.80,0:26:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can you do it? \N - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.24,0:27:02.48,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6E2510&\pos(585.519,187.271)} Hiroki \N 2 years \N 9 months old.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.88,0:26:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still only 2 years and 9 months old.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.88,0:27:00.64,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing. Will he manage it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.64,0:27:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if a car comes?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.32,0:27:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Like this. \N - Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.80,0:27:06.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The answer is correct but...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.06,0:27:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- OK? Go and come back. \N - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.24,0:27:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.24,0:27:11.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just saying go and come back. Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.56,0:27:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.20,0:27:15.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This kid can do it. These are the words \N that the mothers believes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.58,0:27:19.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Anyway, she let him wear his \N pew-pew sound-making shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.06,0:27:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.58,0:27:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.76,0:27:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Bye bye. Take care. \N - Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.18,0:27:28.18,Studio,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.18,0:27:30.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He found something.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.70,0:27:33.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a long branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.88,0:27:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.98,0:27:42.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Pardon me saying this, but it looks more like a baby pretending to fish than a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.08,0:27:44.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll skip fishing and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.52,0:27:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,An ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.20,0:27:50.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An ambulance? No that's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.04,0:27:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,An ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.38,0:27:58.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,, He's not far off.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.38,0:27:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.50,0:28:01.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's not it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.22,0:28:05.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The brain of a 2 year old is looking for the right word.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.60,0:28:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Police car.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.50,0:28:12.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At that age it takes some time to find the right words.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.32,0:28:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The bus that he loves is passing by but going the opposite way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.40,0:28:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.64,0:28:21.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His word finding skills are in top shape now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.58,0:28:27.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While sightseeing Hiroki has managed to walk a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.84,0:28:30.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Moreover, heading straight for the goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.48,0:28:34.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Truth is, he's attempting an errand that's 1 km one-way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.30,0:28:39.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For someone who is 2 years and 9 months old the distance is quite overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.46,0:28:45.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right, the things he was asked to get by his mother are \N sweet curry and Bouten which is a kind of Satsuma-age.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.46,0:28:45.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(310.836,32.171)\fs14} TN: Satsuma-age is a fried fishcake from Kagoshima, Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.68,0:28:49.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was also asked to buy flowers to offer his grandma's house altar.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.24,0:28:52.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will he manage to remember all those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.04,0:28:56.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It has taken 23 minutes for him to arrive at the supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.26,0:28:59.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Which amounts to 2.6 kilometers. That's a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.06,0:29:02.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The door opened but...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.68,0:29:05.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,it closes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.00,0:29:06.34,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's closing. It will close.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.40,0:29:10.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Suddenly distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.28,0:29:15.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What was it I came here for? The gears in his head are grinding.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.76,0:29:23.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yes, he was able to make the connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.18,0:29:25.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I'm here for an errand. \N He runs!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.72,0:29:34.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The 2 year 9 months old started running.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.56,0:29:36.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This doesn't look like curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.64,0:29:40.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He got the Bouten.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.84,0:29:43.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the currry is next?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.58,0:29:47.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Please give me the sweet kind." \N Would be great if he asked as shop attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.82,0:29:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.32,0:29:52.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.06,0:29:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where are the flowers? \N - The flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.94,0:29:55.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.34,0:29:56.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.44,0:30:00.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next up are the flowers, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.60,0:30:05.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Being able to ask for help properly \N is an important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.38,0:30:11.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He always buys flowers for Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.36,0:30:16.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The flowers he will offer his grandma are chrysanthemum.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.24,0:30:22.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He now realizes that he's supposed to get a basket when shopping in the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.68,0:30:26.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He isn't carrying so much that he needs a basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.84,0:30:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hold it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.26,0:30:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.80,0:30:34.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He want's to do it like he always does.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.70,0:30:36.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.06,0:30:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.24,0:30:39.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He hasn't purchased the curry yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.22,0:30:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fine? \N - Yep. \N - Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.52,0:30:43.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,587 yen, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.92,0:30:47.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's forgotten all about the sweet curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.10,0:30:49.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With a 1000 yen bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.10,0:30:50.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Putting it forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.48,0:30:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the 1000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.26,0:30:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,413 yen. Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.44,0:30:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay? Can I put it directly into your bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.32,0:30:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroki will put it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.02,0:31:02.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's putting the change and the receipt in by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.10,0:31:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.94,0:31:18.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What a splendid job. Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.58,0:31:21.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He forgot the curry but this will be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.48,0:31:25.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There is a long way back as well. Do you best.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.16,0:31:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time. The curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.14,0:31:31.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.24,0:31:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot the curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.88,0:31:34.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It just clicked in his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.18,0:31:42.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He knows the way to the curry mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.70,0:31:44.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He just passed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.70,0:31:46.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.58,0:31:52.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Despite it being right here. \N He has no clue after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.40,0:31:56.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As I thought that he returns to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.88,0:32:02.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are all kinds. \N Yes, yes, yes. The sweet one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.82,0:32:09.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The sweet one has the same color as Anpanman's nose.  \N That's what his mother told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.46,0:32:10.20,Studio,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.92,0:32:23.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's bought it all and now it's time to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.36,0:32:27.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The flowers are too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.78,0:32:29.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The flower petals will drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.50,0:32:34.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His nose is already dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.50,0:32:38.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(310.836,32.171)\fs14}TN: In Japanese flowers and nose are homonym and nose dropping means that snot is coming out. It's a play on words.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.04,0:32:44.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now it's time to cross the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.20,0:32:48.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now it's time to bring out the flag that his mother has made.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.38,0:32:51.96,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.62,0:33:00.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Like magic, the cars stopped for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.60,0:33:03.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the expression of love from his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.22,0:33:03.66,Studio,,0,0,0,,Such a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.92,0:33:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.68,0:33:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.80,0:33:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, I brought a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.72,0:33:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought it and came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.02,0:33:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,About the flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.82,0:33:32.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Judging by her reaction the flowers seem to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.34,0:33:35.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,First, hand over the receipt.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.48,0:33:38.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just like a real man.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.62,0:33:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's show this to father.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.96,0:33:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroki, take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.92,0:33:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.94,0:33:48.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,2 years 9 months old and his height is 86 centimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.20,0:33:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Up until there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.42,0:33:57.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today they will offer new flowers to grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.20,0:34:03.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For the sweet curry they will add sweet Kagoshima Satsuma-age.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.68,0:34:09.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Father too grew up on this. Just like how grandma made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.62,0:34:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's say it.  \N - Thank you for this meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.02,0:34:16.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The father is eating a huge amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.40,0:34:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.80,0:34:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it good, Hiroki?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.28,0:34:24.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I got it! I can buy curry if dad isn't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.10,0:34:32.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next up we have someone going on an errand for their own birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.24,0:34:35.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Let's present a 4 year old girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.36,0:34:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.782,292.352)}Aichi ● Okazaki
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.58,0:34:40.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The town of Okazaki where Tokugawa Ieyasu was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.52,0:34:48.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Eight blocks (haccho) west from there lies Haccho Village, where Haccho Miso was created.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.94,0:34:57.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here in this duplex resides Maruya-san, a Miso factory which has continued to make Haccho Miso for the past 670 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.96,0:35:03.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This errand is based upon visiting this traditional miso making village.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.86,0:35:08.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today there is yet another kid who will go on their first errand by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.58,0:35:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.80,0:35:11.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Preparation for pork broth-making.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.78,0:35:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to cut the carrots.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.64,0:35:17.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here is Rikako who will turn 4 today.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.76,0:35:23.16,RedFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(554.662,265.264)\c&HC62698&}Rikako. \N4 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.76,0:35:22.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Overlooking all the children
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.76,0:35:22.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,there is in fact another mother living in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.32,0:35:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And next is...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.70,0:35:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To make pork broth, what else is needed?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.86,0:35:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Miso? \N - Is there miso? Let's have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.90,0:35:31.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.90,0:35:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not enough miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.48,0:35:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's true. \N - What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.92,0:35:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There is some. The pink stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.12,0:35:38.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.82,0:35:40.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That? That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.64,0:35:42.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.96,0:35:46.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The camera is hidden inside a miso box.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.00,0:35:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is miso for konjac.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.42,0:35:50.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.16,0:35:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go purchase miso?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.52,0:35:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yep. \N - I'm sorry to ask you this but...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.52,0:35:58.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The miso we use at home is the golden standard red miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.06,0:36:02.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Haccho miso uses natural fermentation and has a traditional taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.92,0:36:06.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It takes longer to ferment and is much harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.38,0:36:08.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The gold red miso that the mother asked for
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.68,0:36:13.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is easy to use even for the young ones who love haccho miso mixed with rice miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.94,0:36:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Gold? \N - Tell them: "1 kilogram of gold, please."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.62,0:36:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get it?  \N If you look for the old man with the beard he will know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.12,0:36:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay. \N - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.10,0:36:31.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\pos(317.522,22.704)}TN: Tebasaki is fried chicken wings with a sweet and savory glaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.64,0:36:26.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She was also requested to go get the Nagoya famous Tebasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.76,0:36:29.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Because there are many people at home she needs three boxes
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.50,0:36:31.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and golden red miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.50,0:36:36.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Because she always goes with her mother Rikako will recognize the company owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.84,0:36:38.80,Studio,,0,0,0,,- He's so recognizable. \N - Yeah, easy to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.44,0:36:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm heading out. \N - Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.46,0:36:43.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,- Yes. \N - Please use the umbrella properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.86,0:36:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.32,0:36:49.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tonight there will be a party for Rikako who is turning 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.40,0:36:52.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.84,0:36:56.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Rikako who is walking full of energy suddenly becomes drained from energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.92,0:36:58.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The thing that has caught Rikako's eye is
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.92,0:37:03.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,how close the river is from below the guard rail.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.54,0:37:10.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She is always told that if you let your voice out then you will feel energized again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.56,0:37:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hello. \N - Hello. What an amazing person.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.88,0:37:16.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That made her full of energy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.60,0:37:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.68,0:37:22.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Rikako who is going on her first errand \N on her 4th birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.76,0:37:28.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She just arrived at the Nagoya famous Tebasaki shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.74,0:37:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it is open.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.64,0:37:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The door opened but it says they are in the middle of preparation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.04,0:37:36.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(196.796,90.423)}Still preparing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.04,0:37:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.52,0:37:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.98,0:37:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.02,0:37:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Mother? Did you come by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.82,0:37:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- What about your mother? \N - Mom is at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.16,0:37:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- She isn't here? Really? \N - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.68,0:37:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give me 3 boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.38,0:37:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So 3 chicken wings of Tebasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.10,0:37:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You will bring 3 home again?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.10,0:37:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I have money.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.52,0:37:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- You do? Take it out.  \N - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.10,0:38:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,1312 yen, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.10,0:38:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.00,0:38:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for the people who live nearby they sell at noon as an extra service.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.50,0:38:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please wait a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.56,0:38:10.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Nagoya famous Tebasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.18,0:38:12.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Retaining the juiciness of the meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.38,0:38:14.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They've just finished frying.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.38,0:38:17.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sprinkling them with salt and pepper \N and you just can't resist it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.54,0:38:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a little more, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.10,0:38:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make you some delicious ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.08,0:38:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,While you are waiting won't you try this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.64,0:38:29.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The way to eat them is with your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.26,0:38:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.72,0:38:33.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.30,0:38:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please try and eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.02,0:38:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Show everyone at home \N that this is how you hold and eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.40,0:38:42.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. The meat is parting from the bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.02,0:38:45.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What a polite child. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.24,0:38:52.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She arrives at the Maruya-san haccho miso factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.80,0:38:55.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Different from usual she enters from the factory side entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.16,0:38:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there miso here?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.84,0:39:03.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If you want miso then there is a mountains worth of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.60,0:39:06.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She is entering along with the tour group.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.56,0:39:13.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's listening to the explanation with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.16,0:39:13.38,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.38,0:39:14.50,Studio,,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.18,0:39:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The special thing about haccho miso is the low water amount after compressing it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.48,0:39:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,because of how hard we press, squeeze and drain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.46,0:39:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up, let me show you around the way for miso creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.48,0:39:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up, let me show you around the way for miso creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.54,0:39:29.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I see. Haccho miso is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.72,0:39:33.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that they made this great miso close to our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.02,0:39:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The weight of the rocks is about 4 tons and about 6 tons of miso is inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.50,0:39:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were to purchase a bucket of this miso
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.76,0:39:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in a household of 4 people who will drink miso soup once every day
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.94,0:39:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it will take 205 years before you finish drinking it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.30,0:39:48.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wow, 205 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.72,0:39:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please proceed forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.72,0:39:52.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What? What's ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.66,0:39:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? What's inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.34,0:40:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.20,0:40:03.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An unknown old lady helps her see inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.98,0:40:10.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What's up with that? There's nothing in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.82,0:40:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.44,0:40:19.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She comes to buy with mom all the time, but she just watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.16,0:40:22.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That was fun. Alright, I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.82,0:40:25.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's heading for the office where they usually purchase from.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.84,0:40:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the company owner is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.38,0:40:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is so slippery.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.52,0:40:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I came by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.42,0:40:36.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the first time she has come by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.98,0:40:40.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not an automatic door.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.10,0:40:42.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Make sure to close it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.02,0:40:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. 1 kilogram of miso please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.78,0:40:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,1 kilo of miso?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.30,0:40:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.80,0:40:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- What kind of miso would you like? \N - Haccho miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.10,0:40:59.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What? Haccho miso!?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.10,0:41:04.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Though she was told to purchase Akadashi she must've been inspired by all the talk about haccho miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.74,0:41:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You have 1200 yen and that's not enough. \N I will give you the rest as a present, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.14,0:41:12.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Golden red miso is only 1000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.14,0:41:14.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Haccho miso is a bit expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.34,0:41:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She has to put on a hat since they are going into the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.78,0:41:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rinako, did you come by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.48,0:41:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so great of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.78,0:41:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is. Since it's Rikako's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.02,0:41:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How old will you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.02,0:41:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 4 years old. \N - 4 years old? That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.50,0:41:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you came to purchase miso?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.26,0:41:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.70,0:41:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Haccho miso, I wonder what kind of \N amazing taste it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.04,0:41:42.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She is licking the miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.38,0:41:45.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Lifting the lid for the haccho miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.86,0:41:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really hard miso, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.86,0:41:50.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So this is real haccho miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.20,0:41:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.86,0:41:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- A lot? \N - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.74,0:42:00.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's different from usual. \N After hearing the explanation she really wants to dig into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.14,0:42:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we've gathered 1 kilogram.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.32,0:42:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it is your birthday I want to show you what's inside. Do you want to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.40,0:42:13.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The very special service from the company owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.66,0:42:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They've entered a place that is outside of the tour route.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.48,0:42:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There is miso inside of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.12,0:42:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There are stones on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.42,0:42:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there miso where the stones are place upon?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.14,0:42:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, inside of there you will find miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.08,0:42:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it made from stones?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.88,0:42:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So those are edible stones?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.08,0:42:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't eat them. Since they are stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.68,0:42:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Rikako, I want to give you a birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.20,0:42:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's small but...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.20,0:42:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.56,0:42:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those stones?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.62,0:42:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, those are stones. This is wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.06,0:42:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a look. It's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.76,0:42:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.62,0:42:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.92,0:43:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.76,0:43:04.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her curiosity switch has been turned on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.22,0:43:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The type of stone that is placed above the huge bucket.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.78,0:43:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.04,0:43:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you, Rikako?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.36,0:43:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.68,0:43:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to try and taste some miso?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.10,0:43:18.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.10,0:43:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the same as the one you are bringing home today.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.96,0:43:28.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Haccho miso. For the mother it's a bit too bitter but it has a nice traditional taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.82,0:43:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Delicious. \N - Is it delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.70,0:43:33.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.18,0:43:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.78,0:43:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is red miso...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.78,0:43:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is red miso...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.32,0:43:38.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the name of the requested thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.64,0:43:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- I want to eat it. \N - You want to eat it? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.48,0:43:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's delicious. \N - Is it? There's also dengaku miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.48,0:43:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(310.836,32.171)\fs14}TN: Dengaku miso is good for glazing  vegetables and using in oden.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.70,0:43:52.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The last one she gets to try on her observation trip is dengaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.78,0:43:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.00,0:44:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.56,0:44:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.78,0:44:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much to the busy company owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.28,0:44:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to eat miso once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.62,0:44:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You wan't to eat once again before going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.08,0:44:15.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.94,0:44:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She has now sampled all of the miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.36,0:44:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading home.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.20,0:44:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Will you come back again? \N - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.20,0:44:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take care of yourself. \N - Yep. Bye bye. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.56,0:44:36.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For Rikako the taste of haccho miso remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.50,0:44:40.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The taste she remembers. The taste of her home town.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.86,0:44:50.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Obeying the sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.38,0:44:52.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She will soon be back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.74,0:44:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I purchased it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.92,0:45:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You purchased it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.38,0:45:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I even bought the chicken dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.40,0:45:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tha- what!? You bought!?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.08,0:45:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.08,0:45:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.08,0:45:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.20,0:45:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Aaah, it was so heavy. \N - Was it heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.26,0:45:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the company owner's place and...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.68,0:45:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm totally worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.36,0:45:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much. \N You've helped me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.74,0:45:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.48,0:45:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I mistakenly said haccho miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.34,0:45:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You mistakenly said haccho miso?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.84,0:45:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.76,0:45:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.50,0:45:42.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I remembered but haccho miso is alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.24,0:45:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.00,0:45:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.72,0:45:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's delicious, right? \N - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.32,0:45:53.68,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.68,0:45:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.16,0:45:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The house of miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.60,0:45:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it's the house of miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.00,0:45:59.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I see. It's the house of miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.42,0:46:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside of this there is miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.40,0:46:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so the miso is inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.10,0:46:05.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She understands it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.06,0:46:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.32,0:46:09.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everyone has gathered for the 4 year old's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.86,0:46:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday dear Rikako. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.50,0:46:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.72,0:46:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.18,0:46:30.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's pork broth with haccho miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.64,0:46:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the miso that I bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.64,0:46:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- Delicious. \N - It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.24,0:46:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it different from usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.24,0:46:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Haccho miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.24,0:46:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- You bought haccho miso? \N - This is haccho miso?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.12,0:46:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The kid who loves the tebasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.76,0:46:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Higa, you are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.14,0:46:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,About this thing, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.86,0:46:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Without grasping it with chopsticks, you just hold it and eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.10,0:46:59.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She learned it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.70,0:47:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't know then let me teach do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.18,0:47:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.72,0:47:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do it for you. Even for Macchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.38,0:47:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it came out. Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.14,0:47:12.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.74,0:47:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you eat Rikako?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.74,0:47:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.62,0:47:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What a great ending.
